201
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:31,194
A man who would open
her mind to new possibilities...

202
00:11:31,399 --> 00:11:34,197
...and her body to new feelings."

203
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:43,996
You know, there was a time
when l was alone and had no friends.

204
00:11:44,199 --> 00:11:45,518
I'm starting to miss that.

205
00:11:48,640 --> 00:11:51,473
He still hasn't responded.
What's taking him so long?

206
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:54,035
-Do you really want him to write back?
-Yeah, I do.

207
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:57,312
No matter how he responds,
I'm going to destroy him...

208
00:11:57,519 --> 00:12:02,149
...with a picture of a bored cat,
saying "Oh, really?"

209
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:08,155
Mee-wow.

210
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:11,669
What are you doing?

211
00:12:11,879 --> 00:12:16,714
