post positive comments about their paper.

212
00:12:16,920 --> 00:12:21,436
"This wee little bairn of a theory
nearly blew my kilt off"?

213
00:12:21,639 --> 00:12:24,517
No. You have to read it
how Dr. Angus McDoogal...

214
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:27,029
...of the University of Edinburgh would.

215
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:29,276
[SCOTTISH ACCENT]
"This wee little bairn of a theory...

216
00:12:29,439 --> 00:12:31,350
...nearly blew me kilt off."

217
00:12:33,680 --> 00:12:35,238
Oh! He wrote back.

218
00:12:35,439 --> 00:12:38,988
"Cooper and Hofstadter resorting
