given they work at Caltech...

221
00:12:45,680 --> 00:12:51,038
...essentially a technical school where
even the physicists are basically engineers."

222
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:53,117
Engineers?

223
00:12:54,560 --> 00:12:57,279
Do you know how insulting that is?

224
00:12:57,880 --> 00:12:59,279
Yes.

225
00:13:00,079 --> 00:13:03,515
Guys, this person's just going
out of their way to get a rise out of you.

226
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:05,597
Yeah, but it's still so aggravating.

227
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:08,234
All the other comments said nice things.
Focus on those.

228
00:13:08,439 --> 00:13:13,832
Yeah. Dr. Dmitri Plancovik
of Moscow University said:

229
00:13:14,040 --> 00:13:17,715
[RUSSIAN ACCENT] "This paper great.
I love it more than vodka."

230
00:13:19,439 --> 00:13:21,873
See? Better with the accent.

231
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:25,274
-And send.
-What did you write?

232
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:28,517
I'm done hiding from bullies.
I am taking this into the real world.

233
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:31,234
-What does that mean?
-I told him we'll meet face-to-face.

234
00:13:31,439 --> 00:13:32,508
Anytime, anywhere.

235
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:35,359
